-content/uploads/2021/06/10065916/bicycle-sunshade-canopy-yellow-503x420.jpg 503w\"></a></p><p>The canopy is made of a lightweight mesh material, designed to protect the rider from the elements; whether that be the scorching heat of the mid-day sun, or the deluges of monsoon season.</p><p>It has a universal fitment, clamping to the seat tube of just about any bicycle; it is said to be easy to attach and detach. We don’t have a claimed weight the contraption but the company do say it is lightweight and portable, with an adjustable, foldable design.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue.jpg\" alt=\"bicycle sun shade blue canopy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1001\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue-297x248.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue-800x667.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue-120x100.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue-768x641.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue-696x581.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue-1068x891.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue-503x420.jpg 503w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue-297x248.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue-800x667.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue-120x100.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue-768x641.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue-696x581.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue-1068x891.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10065922/blue-bicycle-sunshade-blue-503x420.jpg 503w\"></a></p><p>The Bicycle Sun Shade does come with a number of warnings; it is not to be used in windy conditions, it is not to be used for mountain biking or stunt riding, and riders should take care to keep an eye out for low hanging objects. They also say it is not designed to replace a helmet, though we note their promo video features cyclists riding without one.</p><h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3><p>The Bicycle Sun Shade is available with a blue or yellow canopy and retails at $119 USD.</p><p><a href=\"https://bicyclesunshade.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>BicycleSunShade.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"fd4195303bacfeab4634e635419d82a1d2dd3f809ce94f84749a084b717c85cb","category":"Cycling"}